## Chapter 04 : MPI Programming in Python

## 1 alltoall.py
What I learned

Is program me All-to-All communication hoti hai. Har process baaki sab processes ko data send karta hai aur sab se data receive bhi karta hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python alltoall.py
Use

Distributed systems jahan sab processes ek dusre se data exchange karte hain

When use

Jab har process ko sab processes ke saath communication karni ho

Summary

MPI me all-to-all data exchange show karta hai

Advantages

Fast parallel communication
Good for distributed systems

Disadvantages

High communication cost

## 2 broadcast.py
What I learned

Is program me ek process apna data sab processes ko share karta hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python broadcast.py
Use

Same data ko multiple processes tak pohanchana

When use

Jab ek process ka data sab ko chahiye ho

Summary

MPI broadcast operation

Advantages

Fast data sharing
Simple method

Disadvantages

Sirf ek source process hota hai

## 3 deadLockProblems.py
What I learned

Is program me deadlock situation samjhayi gayi hai jahan processes galat order me send/receive karte hain aur system freeze ho jata hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 6 python deadLockProblems.py
Use

MPI synchronization aur deadlock understanding

When use

Safe communication patterns seekhne ke liye

Summary

Deadlock problems explain karta hai

Advantages

Process synchronization samajh aati hai

Disadvantages

Galat sequence se program freeze ho sakta hai

## 4 gather.py
What I learned

Is program me sab processes ka data ek root process me collect hota hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python gather.py
Use

Multiple processes ka result collect karna

When use

Jab distributed results ko combine karna ho

Summary

MPI gather operation

Advantages

Efficient result collection

Disadvantages

Root process overload ho sakta hai

## 5 helloWorld_MPI.py
What I learned

Basic MPI program jahan har process apna rank print karta hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python helloWorld_MPI.py
Use

MPI basics samajhne ke liye

When use

Initialization aur process identification seekhne ke liye

Summary

Simple MPI hello world program

Advantages

Easy for beginners

Disadvantages

Communication nahi hoti

## 6 pointToPointCommunication.py
What I learned

Is program me ek process directly dusre process ko data send karta hai aur receive karta hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 9 python pointToPointCommunication.py
Use

Direct process-to-process communication

When use

Jab specific processes ke darmiyan data exchange ho

Summary

Point-to-point communication in MPI

Advantages

Simple communication model

Disadvantages

Large systems me manage karna mushkil

## 7 reduction.py
What I learned

Is program me sab processes ka data combine hota hai (jaise SUM operation).

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python reduction.py
Use

Parallel computation ka final result nikalna

When use

Jab sab processes ka output merge karna ho

Summary

MPI reduction operation

Advantages

Efficient aggregation

Disadvantages

Root dependency hoti hai

## 8 scatter.py
What I learned

Is program me ek process data ko multiple processes me divide karke distribute karta hai.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python scatter.py
Use

Workload distribution

When use

Large data ko parallel process karna ho

Summary

MPI scatter operation

Advantages

Efficient task distribution

Disadvantages

Proper data splitting zaroori hai

## 9 virtualTopology.py
What I learned

Is program me processes ko grid (cartesian structure) me arrange kiya jata hai jahan neighbors define hote hain.

How to execute
mpiexec -n 4 python virtualTopology.py
Use

Scientific computing aur grid-based simulations

When use

Jab structured communication pattern chahiye ho

Summary

Virtual topology in MPI

Advantages

Organized communication
Useful for simulations

Disadvantages

Beginners ke liye complex